				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				hello all, i am lvl 22 necro on druzzil ro server, and i got the gbs yesterday morning, at about 5 or 6 am hawaii time.  i got over to the ruins just before it started getting dark, and i immediately had pet start killing everything inside the ruins and in the immediate vicinity.  i didn't med at all, if i needed mana, i just cast dark pact on myself, and lifesiphoned to regain hp.  MAYBE not medding right there has something to do with it, who knows.  ANYWAYS, it was very late in the game night, and i was fighting 2 or 3 skeles in the middle of the ruins, and all of a sudden pyzjin attacked me, i have no idea if she spawned in the ruins, or came walking in.  all i know is that i beat her like she stole something from me...she was easy!  her pet has tons more hp than she does.  i looted, and almost had a heart attack when i saw the 8 ball looking gbs on her corpse.  it took me maybe an hour all told.  i guess i am lucky!!  good luck to all of you, i think it is just random and luck...i don't think there are triggers to coerce her into spawning.
